metadata.name: Summer Love
metadata.description:
Two lovers embrace in the heat of summer.  

This photo was captured on the edge of sunset on a beach in Aruba during the Summer of 2022.  I was in the middle of dinner when I noticed the sky lit up with a fiery glow.  I can never resist a beautiful sky, so I quickly excused myself and ran over to capture the scene.  When I arrived, this couple was standing together on the beach's lone pier, sharing a moment together in paradise.
